      <p>We are an organization dedicatged to improving women's healthcare.  We partner with laboratories by providing rare and hard to find samples that are used to develop laboraotry tests and new technologies in maternal/fetal medicine.  By donating blood samples after a confirmed high-risk NIPT laboratory test, you help advance genetic testing in women's health—and receive meaningful financial compensation for your time and participation.</p>
