      <h2>🧬 What is NIPT?</h2>
      <p>Non-Invasive Prenatal Testing (NIPT) is a blood test that screens for chromosomal conditions like Down syndrome. It analyzes fetal DNA in the mother’s blood and helps families recieve important .</p>
